3283void QTextEngine::resolveFormats() const
3284{
3285 if (!specialData || specialData->formats.isEmpty())
3286 return;
3287 Q_ASSERT(specialData->resolvedFormats.isEmpty());
3288
3289 QTextFormatCollection *collection = formatCollection();
3290
3291 QList<QTextCharFormat> resolvedFormats(layoutData->items.size());
3292
3293 QVarLengthArray<int, 64> formatsSortedByStart;
3294 formatsSortedByStart.reserve(sz: specialData->formats.size());
3295 for (int i = 0; i < specialData->formats.size(); ++i) {
3296 if (specialData->formats.at(i).length >= 0)
3297 formatsSortedByStart.append(t: i);
3298 }
3299 QVarLengthArray<int, 64> formatsSortedByEnd = formatsSortedByStart;
3300 std::sort(first: formatsSortedByStart.begin(), last: formatsSortedByStart.end(),
3301 comp: FormatRangeComparatorByStart(specialData->formats));
3302 std::sort(first: formatsSortedByEnd.begin(), last: formatsSortedByEnd.end(),
3303 comp: FormatRangeComparatorByEnd(specialData->formats));
3304
3305 QVarLengthArray<int, 16> currentFormats;
3306 const int *startIt = formatsSortedByStart.constBegin();
3307 const int *endIt = formatsSortedByEnd.constBegin();
3308
3309 for (int i = 0; i < layoutData->items.size(); ++i) {
3310 const QScriptItem *si = &layoutData->items.at(i);
3311 int end = si->position + length(si);
3312
3313 while (startIt != formatsSortedByStart.constEnd() &&
3314 specialData->formats.at(i: *startIt).start <= si->position) {
3315 currentFormats.insert(before: std::upper_bound(first: currentFormats.begin(), last: currentFormats.end(), val: *startIt),
3316 x: *startIt);
3317 ++startIt;
3318 }
3319 while (endIt != formatsSortedByEnd.constEnd() &&
3320 specialData->formats.at(i: *endIt).start + specialData->formats.at(i: *endIt).length < end) {
3321 int *currentFormatIterator = std::lower_bound(currentFormats.begin(), currentFormats.end(), *endIt);
3322 if (*endIt < *currentFormatIterator)
3323 currentFormatIterator = currentFormats.end();
3324 currentFormats.remove(i: currentFormatIterator - currentFormats.begin());
3325 ++endIt;
3326 }
3327
3328 QTextCharFormat &format = resolvedFormats[i];
3329 if (QTextDocumentPrivate::get(block) != nullptr) {
3330 // when we have a QTextDocumentPrivate, formatIndex might still return a valid index based
3331 // on the preeditPosition. for all other cases, we cleared the resolved format indices
3332 format = collection->charFormat(index: formatIndex(si));
3333 }
3334 if (!currentFormats.isEmpty()) {
3335 for (int cur : currentFormats) {
3336 const QTextLayout::FormatRange &range = specialData->formats.at(i: cur);
3337 Q_ASSERT(range.start <= si->position && range.start + range.length >= end);
3338 format.merge(other: range.format);
3339 }
3340 format = collection->charFormat(index: collection->indexForFormat(f: format)); // get shared copy

3374QFixed QTextEngine::offsetInLigature(const QScriptItem *si, int pos, int max, int glyph_pos)
3375{
3376 unsigned short *logClusters = this->logClusters(si);
3377 const QGlyphLayout &glyphs = shapedGlyphs(si);
3378
3379 int offsetInCluster = 0;
3380 for (int i = pos - 1; i >= 0; i--) {
3381 if (logClusters[i] == glyph_pos)
3382 offsetInCluster++;
3383 else
3384 break;
3385 }
3386
3387 // in the case that the offset is inside a (multi-character) glyph,
3388 // interpolate the position.
3389 if (offsetInCluster > 0) {
3390 int clusterLength = 0;
3391 for (int i = pos - offsetInCluster; i < max; i++) {
3392 if (logClusters[i] == glyph_pos)
3393 clusterLength++;
3394 else
3395 break;
3396 }
3397 if (clusterLength)
3398 return glyphs.advances[glyph_pos] * offsetInCluster / clusterLength;
3399 }
3400
3401 return 0;
3402}

3404// Scan in logClusters[from..to-1] for glyph_pos
3405int QTextEngine::getClusterLength(unsigned short *logClusters,
3406 const QCharAttributes *attributes,
3407 int from, int to, int glyph_pos, int *start)
3408{
3409 int clusterLength = 0;
3410 for (int i = from; i < to; i++) {
3411 if (logClusters[i] == glyph_pos && attributes[i].graphemeBoundary) {
3412 if (*start < 0)
3413 *start = i;
3414 clusterLength++;
3415 }
3416 else if (clusterLength)
3417 break;
3418 }
3419 return clusterLength;
3420}
3421
3422int QTextEngine::positionInLigature(const QScriptItem *si, int end,
3423 QFixed x, QFixed edge, int glyph_pos,
3424 bool cursorOnCharacter)
3425{
3426 unsigned short *logClusters = this->logClusters(si);
3427 int clusterStart = -1;
3428 int clusterLength = 0;
3429
3430 if (si->analysis.script != QChar::Script_Common &&
3431 si->analysis.script != QChar::Script_Greek &&
3432 si->analysis.script != QChar::Script_Latin &&
3433 si->analysis.script != QChar::Script_Hiragana &&
3434 si->analysis.script != QChar::Script_Katakana &&
3435 si->analysis.script != QChar::Script_Bopomofo &&
3436 si->analysis.script != QChar::Script_Han) {
3437 if (glyph_pos == -1)
3438 return si->position + end;
3439 else {
3440 int i;
3441 for (i = 0; i < end; i++)
3442 if (logClusters[i] == glyph_pos)
3443 break;
3444 return si->position + i;
3445 }
3446 }
3447
3448 if (glyph_pos == -1 && end > 0)
3449 glyph_pos = logClusters[end - 1];
3450 else {
3451 if (x <= edge)
3452 glyph_pos--;
3453 }
3454
3455 const QCharAttributes *attrs = attributes() + si->position;
3456 logClusters = this->logClusters(si);
3457 clusterLength = getClusterLength(logClusters, attributes: attrs, from: 0, to: end, glyph_pos, start: &clusterStart);
3458
3459 if (clusterLength) {
3460 const QGlyphLayout &glyphs = shapedGlyphs(si);
3461 QFixed glyphWidth = glyphs.effectiveAdvance(item: glyph_pos);
3462 // the approximate width of each individual element of the ligature
3463 QFixed perItemWidth = glyphWidth / clusterLength;
3464 if (perItemWidth <= 0)
3465 return si->position + clusterStart;
3466 QFixed left = x > edge ? edge : edge - glyphWidth;
3467 int n = ((x - left) / perItemWidth).floor().toInt();
3468 QFixed dist = x - left - n * perItemWidth;
3469 int closestItem = dist > (perItemWidth / 2) ? n + 1 : n;
3470 if (cursorOnCharacter && closestItem > 0)
3471 closestItem--;
3472 int pos = clusterStart + closestItem;
3473 // Jump to the next grapheme boundary
3474 while (pos < end && !attrs[pos].graphemeBoundary)
3475 pos++;
3476 return si->position + pos;
3477 }
3478 return si->position + end;
3479}

3567int QTextEngine::positionAfterVisualMovement(int pos, QTextCursor::MoveOperation op)
3568{
3569 itemize();
3570
3571 bool moveRight = (op == QTextCursor::Right);
3572 bool alignRight = isRightToLeft();
3573 if (!layoutData->hasBidi)
3574 return moveRight ^ alignRight ? nextLogicalPosition(oldPos: pos) : previousLogicalPosition(oldPos: pos);
3575
3576 int lineNum = lineNumberForTextPosition(pos);
3577 if (lineNum < 0)
3578 return pos;
3579
3580 const auto insertionPoints = insertionPointsForLine(lineNum);
3581 for (size_t i = 0, max = insertionPoints.size(); i < max; ++i)
3582 if (pos == insertionPoints[i]) {
3583 if (moveRight) {
3584 if (i + 1 < max)
3585 return insertionPoints[i + 1];
3586 } else {
3587 if (i > 0)
3588 return insertionPoints[i - 1];
3589 }
3590
3591 if (moveRight ^ alignRight) {
3592 if (lineNum + 1 < lines.size())
3593 return alignRight ? endOfLine(lineNum: lineNum + 1) : beginningOfLine(lineNum: lineNum + 1);
3594 }
3595 else {
3596 if (lineNum > 0)
3597 return alignRight ? beginningOfLine(lineNum: lineNum - 1) : endOfLine(lineNum: lineNum - 1);
3598 }
3599
3600 break;
3601 }
3602
3603 return pos;
3604}

3664void QTextEngine::adjustUnderlines()
3665{
3666 // qDebug() << __PRETTY_FUNCTION__ << underlineList.count() << "underlines";
3667 if (underlineList.isEmpty())
3668 return;
3669
3670 ItemDecorationList::iterator start = underlineList.begin();
3671 ItemDecorationList::iterator end = underlineList.end();
3672 ItemDecorationList::iterator it = start;
3673 qreal underlinePos = start->y;
3674 qreal penWidth = start->pen.widthF();
3675 qreal lastLineEnd = start->x1;
3676
3677 while (it != end) {
3678 if (qFuzzyCompare(p1: lastLineEnd, p2: it->x1)) { // no gap between underlines
3679 underlinePos = qMax(a: underlinePos, b: it->y);
3680 penWidth = qMax(a: penWidth, b: it->pen.widthF());
3681 } else { // gap between this and the last underline
3682 adjustUnderlines(start, end: it, underlinePos, penWidth);
3683 start = it;
3684 underlinePos = start->y;
3685 penWidth = start->pen.widthF();
3686 }
3687 lastLineEnd = it->x2;
3688 ++it;
3689 }
3690
3691 adjustUnderlines(start, end, underlinePos, penWidth);
3692}

3807
3808 m.x = QFixed::fromReal(r: l.x1());
3809 m.y = QFixed::fromReal(r: l.y1());
3810
3811 // The offset is relative to the baseline which is why we use dx/dy of the line
3812 m.xoff = QFixed::fromReal(r: l.dx());
3813 m.yoff = QFixed::fromReal(r: l.dy());
3814
3815 return m;
3816}

3818QTextLineItemIterator::QTextLineItemIterator(QTextEngine *_eng, int _lineNum, const QPointF &pos,
3819 const QTextLayout::FormatRange *_selection)
3820 : eng(_eng),
3821 line(eng->lines[_lineNum]),
3822 si(nullptr),
3823 lineNum(_lineNum),
3824 lineEnd(line.from + line.length),
3825 firstItem(eng->findItem(strPos: line.from)),
3826 lastItem(eng->findItem(strPos: lineEnd - 1, firstItem)),
3827 nItems((firstItem >= 0 && lastItem >= firstItem)? (lastItem-firstItem+1) : 0),
3828 logicalItem(-1),
3829 item(-1),
3830 visualOrder(nItems),
3831 selection(_selection)
3832{
3833 x = QFixed::fromReal(r: pos.x());
3834
3835 x += line.x;
3836
3837 x += eng->alignLine(line);
3838
3839 if (nItems > 0) {
3840 QVarLengthArray<uchar> levels(nItems);
3841 for (int i = 0; i < nItems; ++i)
3842 levels[i] = eng->layoutData->items.at(i: i + firstItem).analysis.bidiLevel;
3843 QTextEngine::bidiReorder(numItems: nItems, levels: levels.data(), visualOrder: visualOrder.data());
3844 }
3845
3846 eng->shapeLine(line);
3847}
3848
3849QScriptItem &QTextLineItemIterator::next()
3850{
3851 x += itemWidth;
3852
3853 ++logicalItem;
3854 item = visualOrder[logicalItem] + firstItem;
3855 itemLength = eng->length(item);
3856 si = &eng->layoutData->items[item];
3857 if (!si->num_glyphs)
3858 eng->shape(item);
3859
3860 itemStart = qMax(a: line.from, b: si->position);
3861 itemEnd = qMin(a: lineEnd, b: si->position + itemLength);
3862
3863 if (si->analysis.flags >= QScriptAnalysis::TabOrObject) {
3864 glyphsStart = 0;
3865 glyphsEnd = 1;
3866 itemWidth = si->width;
3867 return *si;
3868 }
3869
3870 unsigned short *logClusters = eng->logClusters(si);
3871 QGlyphLayout glyphs = eng->shapedGlyphs(si);
3872
3873 glyphsStart = logClusters[itemStart - si->position];
3874 glyphsEnd = (itemEnd == si->position + itemLength) ? si->num_glyphs : logClusters[itemEnd - si->position];
3875
3876 // show soft-hyphen at line-break
3877 if (si->position + itemLength >= lineEnd
3878 && eng->layoutData->string.at(i: lineEnd - 1).unicode() == QChar::SoftHyphen)
3879 glyphs.attributes[glyphsEnd - 1].dontPrint = false;
3880
3881 itemWidth = 0;
3882 for (int g = glyphsStart; g < glyphsEnd; ++g)
3883 itemWidth += glyphs.effectiveAdvance(item: g);
3884
3885 return *si;
3886}

3888bool QTextLineItemIterator::getSelectionBounds(QFixed *selectionX, QFixed *selectionWidth) const
3889{
3890 *selectionX = *selectionWidth = 0;
3891
3892 if (!selection)
3893 return false;
3894
3895 if (si->analysis.flags >= QScriptAnalysis::TabOrObject) {
3896 if (si->position >= selection->start + selection->length
3897 || si->position + itemLength <= selection->start)
3898 return false;
3899
3900 *selectionX = x;
3901 *selectionWidth = itemWidth;
3902 } else {
3903 unsigned short *logClusters = eng->logClusters(si);
3904 QGlyphLayout glyphs = eng->shapedGlyphs(si);
3905
3906 int from = qMax(a: itemStart, b: selection->start) - si->position;
3907 int to = qMin(a: itemEnd, b: selection->start + selection->length) - si->position;
3908 if (from >= to)
3909 return false;
3910
3911 int start_glyph = logClusters[from];
3912 int end_glyph = (to == itemLength) ? si->num_glyphs : logClusters[to];
3913 QFixed soff;
3914 QFixed swidth;
3915 if (si->analysis.bidiLevel %2) {
3916 for (int g = glyphsEnd - 1; g >= end_glyph; --g)
3917 soff += glyphs.effectiveAdvance(item: g);
3918 for (int g = end_glyph - 1; g >= start_glyph; --g)
3919 swidth += glyphs.effectiveAdvance(item: g);
3920 } else {
3921 for (int g = glyphsStart; g < start_glyph; ++g)
3922 soff += glyphs.effectiveAdvance(item: g);
3923 for (int g = start_glyph; g < end_glyph; ++g)
3924 swidth += glyphs.effectiveAdvance(item: g);
3925 }
3926
3927 // If the starting character is in the middle of a ligature,
3928 // selection should only contain the right part of that ligature
3929 // glyph, so we need to get the width of the left part here and
3930 // add it to *selectionX
3931 QFixed leftOffsetInLigature = eng->offsetInLigature(si, pos: from, max: to, glyph_pos: start_glyph);
3932 *selectionX = x + soff + leftOffsetInLigature;
3933 *selectionWidth = swidth - leftOffsetInLigature;
3934 // If the ending character is also part of a ligature, swidth does
3935 // not contain that part yet, we also need to find out the width of
3936 // that left part
3937 *selectionWidth += eng->offsetInLigature(si, pos: to, max: itemLength, glyph_pos: end_glyph);
3938 }
3939 return true;
3940}
